{"opinion":{"isContribuable":false,"votes_total":7,"arguments_yes_count":0,"arguments_no_count":1,"id":462,"created_at":"2015-10-07T20:19:01+0200","updated_at":"2015-10-07T20:19:01+0200","body":"<p>L&#39;&Eacute;tat est garant de l&#39;acc&egrave;s aux soins sur tout le territoire national.Cependant les d&eacute;serts m&eacute;dicaux se multiplient. La t&eacute;l&eacute;m&eacute;decine est une des r&eacute;ponses &agrave; ce probl&egrave;me.L&#39;&Eacute;tat soutiendra son essor en s&#39;appuyant sur des plateformes fran&ccedil;aises multi-sp&eacute;cialit&eacute;s de t&eacute;l&eacute;m&eacute;decine et en encourageant la cr&eacute;ation d&#39;actes rembours&eacute;s par l&#39;Assurance Maladie.<\/p>","versions_count":0,"sources_count":0,"arguments_count":1,"author":{"username":"philippe bonnet","displayName":"philippe bonnet","uniqueId":"philippebonnet1","isAdmin":false,"media":null,"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/philippebonnet1","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}},"type":{"id":103,"title":"Section 1","subtitle":"Comp\u00e9tences et organisation","voteWidgetType":2,"votesHelpText":"Pensez-vous que cette proposition permet d'atteindre les objectifs pr\u00e9sent\u00e9s dans l\u2019explication de l\u2019article ?","commentSystem":2,"color":"blue","versionable":true,"sourceable":true,"votesThreshold":null,"votesThresholdHelpText":null},"sources":[],"arguments":[{"isContribuable":false,"id":4468,"body":"R\u00e9publique num\u00e9rique, oui, mais pas au d\u00e9triment du contact humain. Plut\u00f4t encourager les m\u00e9decins \u00e0 s'installer \u00e0 la campagne.","created_at":"2015-10-15T23:18:53+0200","updated_at":"2015-10-15T23:18:53+0200","is_enabled":true,"votes_count":0,"type":0,"is_trashed":false,"author":{"username":"Christophe De Natale","displayName":"Christophe De Natale","uniqueId":"christophedenatale","isAdmin":false,"media":null,"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/christophedenatale","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}},"_links":{"show":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/consultations\/projet-de-loi-numerique\/consultation\/consultation\/opinions\/section-1-competences-et-organisation\/developper-la-medecine-numerique#arg-4468","edit":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/consultations\/projet-de-loi-numerique\/consultation\/consultation\/opinions\/section-1-competences-et-organisation\/developper-la-medecine-numerique\/arguments\/4468\/edit","report":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/consultations\/projet-de-loi-numerique\/consultation\/consultation\/opinions\/section-1-competences-et-organisation\/developper-la-medecine-numerique\/arguments\/4468\/report"},"has_user_voted":false,"has_user_reported":false}],"modals":[],"votes":[{"user":{"username":"k\u00e9vin","displayName":"k\u00e9vin","uniqueId":"kevin1","isAdmin":false,"media":null,"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/kevin1","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}}},{"user":{"username":"Jeanne Varasco","displayName":"Jeanne Varasco","uniqueId":"jeannevarasco","isAdmin":false,"media":{"url":"\/media\/cache\/default_avatar\/default\/0001\/01\/139_default_avatar.jpg"},"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/jeannevarasco","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}}},{"user":{"username":"Vincent Reverdy","displayName":"Vincent Reverdy","uniqueId":"vincentreverdy","isAdmin":false,"media":{"url":"\/media\/cache\/default_avatar\/default\/0001\/01\/268_default_avatar.jpg"},"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/vincentreverdy","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}}},{"user":{"username":"Christophe De Natale","displayName":"Christophe De Natale","uniqueId":"christophedenatale","isAdmin":false,"media":null,"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/christophedenatale","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}}},{"user":{"username":"Yann Leroux","displayName":"Yann Leroux","uniqueId":"yannleroux","isAdmin":false,"media":null,"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/yannleroux","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}}}],"appendices":[{"body":"<p>La t&eacute;l&eacute;m&eacute;decine (ou plut&ocirc;t la m&eacute;decine num&eacute;rique) est une des r&eacute;ponses &agrave; la multiplication des d&eacute;serts m&eacute;dicaux. Malheureusement, elle ne se d&eacute;veloppe pas en France en raison du manque de reconnaissance de l&#39;Assurance Maladie (un seul acte rembours&eacute; &agrave; ce jour, pour le d&eacute;pistage de la r&eacute;tinopathie diab&eacute;tique). L&#39;&Eacute;tat doit favoriser son essor en s&#39;appuyant sur des plateformes fran&ccedil;aises multi-sp&eacute;cialit&eacute;s(radiologie,ophtalmologie,cardiologie,dermatologie, dentisterie) et en encourageant la cr&eacute;ation d&#39;actes rembours&eacute;s par l&#39;Assurance Maladie.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p>La m&eacute;decine n&#39;&eacute;chappe pas &agrave; la transformation num&eacute;rique du monde. L&#39;&Eacute;tat doit favoriser l&#39;&eacute;mergence d&#39;une fili&egrave;re fran&ccedil;aise de m&eacute;decine num&eacute;rique qui peut devenir leader mondial et repr&eacute;senter une alternative &agrave; l&#39;arriv&eacute;e prochaine des grands op&eacute;rateurs nord-am&eacute;ricains.<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>","type":{"title":"Explication de l'article"}}],"ranking":506,"is_trashed":false,"title":"D\u00e9velopper la m\u00e9decine num\u00e9rique.","votes_nok":3,"votes_ok":3,"votes_mitige":1,"_links":{"show":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/consultations\/projet-de-loi-numerique\/consultation\/consultation\/opinions\/section-1-competences-et-organisation\/developper-la-medecine-numerique","edit":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/consultations\/projet-de-loi-numerique\/consultation\/consultation\/opinions\/section-1-competences-et-organisation\/developper-la-medecine-numerique\/edit","report":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/consultations\/projet-de-loi-numerique\/consultation\/consultation\/opinions\/section-1-competences-et-organisation\/developper-la-medecine-numerique\/report","type":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/consultations\/projet-de-loi-numerique\/consultation\/consultation\/opinions\/section-1-competences-et-organisation"},"user_vote":null,"has_user_reported":false},"rankingThreshold":null,"opinionTerm":1}